Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.32,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All I want！Only you！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:04.12,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,どんなやり込み要素を盛り込んでいても
