Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.12,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,こうじゃないと言いたいハッピーエンド
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.75,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}意味不明の世迷い言を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.09,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}空想だった感情が現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.59,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Ah！Cool！ You’re cool！Beautiful！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:22.30,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}平穏だった日常が乱雑に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.60,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I can’t believe！ You have to leave！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.64,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,10)\fad(200,200)}好きも
